Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日庙会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞到哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手湿湿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是夏日庙会的传单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到开夏日庙会的时期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从儿时起每年都去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬神轿  还有庙会上的焰火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…火？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年去不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  到泳池后我们来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  我绝对不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  我呢  稍微能游一游了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了  今天是高中的上学日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所现在在放暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又一边看手机一边走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再慢慢吞吞的可是会迟到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子刚说完你就输给夏日庙会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动  老子现在要卯足劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我弄干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件制服是圣南女子学院的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识小夏小姐吗  藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是女子大学的附属高中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是清花小姐和千岁小姐的母校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的还真清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是与你无缘的大小姐学校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托儿所放暑假的期间  他也一直在忙着打工和学习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  已经干了  去把这手帕还了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏小姐不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点太阳就下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事会在第二学期开始时正式公布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水桥夏树同学担任代表的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿者俱乐部发起的美化活动获得了认可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次  县里向我校送来了感谢信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏小姐的名字叫做水桥夏树呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌倒的家伙也在同一个班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家注意  就算是暑假  也不要熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假往往会使人精神松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的行为举止要符合圣南女子学院学生的规范…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森川同学  又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不收敛点我就没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  现在确认一下暑假中的紧急联系人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  拍的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点自信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来请打扫泳池的值日生到泳池边集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的学生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是艾草托儿所的花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托儿所？你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的同学  快去把事务员叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦  小鸠  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之必须找到夏树小姐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿好镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是实物好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃你不是也马上就能买了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩  是早上和小夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是叫雪乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花户小鸠把手帕拿来还你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不过我没有电熨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皱巴巴的  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你言重了  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池的打扫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  没对小夏说过  我现在在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工是校规禁止的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:08:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃正为买相机在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池打扫我们会帮忙的  今天就请你睁一只眼闭一只眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…夏树小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小鸠也一起帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如藤本先生所说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是与我无缘的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来  突然说要一起帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信的搭讪方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭讪？那个很难以置信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…突然向你搭讪了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正好不太想一个人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像雪乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学时的夏日庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很要好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说…曾经很要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不再要好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  雪乃躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面衬衣露出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你弄好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前每天早上都一起去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃头发好乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  快点回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知从何时起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小夏  我又睡过头了  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入高中后就渐渐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  小夏  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  你要是对摄影有兴趣的话就加入我们社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我对社团活动不太…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛  就算来参观一下也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  我们两人已经完全是各干各的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃她…在想什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:12:17.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮夏树小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么帮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道搞屁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先去见见雪乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  这下总算能赶上庙会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑你喜欢的吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  妨碍你打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  已经结束了  别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱也攒够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天终于可以在站前大厦的特卖会上买相机了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天拿的不就是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想有一个自己的  所以一直在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊  雪乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是从手机拍照开始的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在完全沉浸其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和摄影社的朋友也变得很要好  非常谈得来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不和夏树小姐说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏是我以前的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我们去买手机挂件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要和夏树一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连手机挂件都一样的话就搞不清是谁的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我叫夏树  所以是西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃的是雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们互换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和夏树不再要好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌她了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事…我不会讨厌小夏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小夏她…是我的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  多不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次让我好好拍一张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等雪乃的拍摄技术有长进了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树小姐和雪乃小姐其实都想和对方好好相处的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们本人都不明白  我们又怎么可能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…总想为她们做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请问特卖中的相机店在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相机店的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  等回去了马上试拍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单眼反光式相机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…雪乃她很努力地打工  买了一个好相机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们摄影社的都觉得羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃你就加入摄影社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作雪乃首次购买单反相机的纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得买了梦寐以求的相机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  下次去摄影会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃这么有才能  一定能拍出好照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影这种事  只要模仿广告的构图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就会有模有样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人会因此而产生错觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃也搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有才能  还自以为是专业人士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有才能就好了…我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在觉得摄影很有趣…很喜欢相机…仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能买到最喜欢的相机  真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  能让我一个人静一静吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会说那种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了…挂件不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:17:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这回去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才果然还是夏树小姐不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必须去说她两句才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了  挂件不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里我也都找过好几次了  还是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我对雪乃说了过分的话  所以挂件才会不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃小姐和夏树小姐其实还是很要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…说不定是在害怕雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…那一定是因为雪乃小姐努力的样子太过耀眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃过去一直就有些不同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时我会觉得她离我很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛会被她甩下  这让我很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我只能选择在学习和其他事情上拼命努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先开始疏远雪乃的人…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树小姐  可以借我电话用一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（对不起  附件1件）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏  你还留着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我说了很过分的话  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…一直留着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直留着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师和千岁小姐没有吵过架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架这种事  多到数不清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩谁都不理谁的情况有过好几次不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  的确有过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你们两人还是很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏  笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  多不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰火好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  今天给你90分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧  你这小贼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰火好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被夏日庙会治愈了怎么行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是给你-200分好了  土鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰火好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
